title: Jones Named MIC Co-Newcomer of the Week - NewsBreak
text:
By Via Illinois State University Athletics, ,
1 days ago NORMAL, Ill. â€“ The Illinois State gymnastics team is two meets into the 2025 season, and it is already receiving stellar performances from a key newcomer in transfer Jaly Jones who was named the Midwest Independent Conference Co-Newcomer of the Week on Wednesday by the conference. Jones shared the weekly honor with Kyleigh Ghanbari of Texas Woman's in the first awards presentation of the year. The Redbirds posted a second-place finish last week and recorded a season-high score of 195.100 at the Next Level Gymnastics Podium Challenge in Battle Creek, Michigan.
